data.title: Yogi Babu team up for Periyandavar
data.meta_description: Read this exciting story from The New Indian Express May 19, 2022. Director R Kannan of Jayam Kondaan fame is teaming up with Yogi Babu for his 12th film which is titled Periyandavar.
